column4: NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "3984145E46858CDB17B3589D15CF8159", "He he, I\'ll crash the bad computer! He he he!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "83304FA640F07C2A86DD2FB24BCBED03", "He\'s the one... Hey! Hey, what are you doing?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "8F28CC294575C6A6622B808950EBB849", "Yeah! I\'ll destroy! I\'ll destroy everything. All bad things!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "65149DBC4C916E9C1852429C2B77501A", "Oh no, he\'s crazy. He is an Ultimate Digimon, but, we have to stop him!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "F1CD607B40342F99C06E6A847BC4AF34", "He he he, I\'ll destroy you all!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "492921D44336661E6DF349950FA84A97", "We\'re losing electricity. Let\'s ask Andromon to stop the factory waste water.")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "1B58FB4549B1556D8D8E7C9A06DF2BA6", "The factory\'s closed now, so I have lots of free time. I\'ll help you!")
NSLOCTEXT("[B79A11384B5A4348F7D438B360FE4332]", "414D84F94E1FA76FFA6888A6ADE47288", "He regained his senses, but he still looks insane!? still looks insane!")
